The number of German tourists visiting SA jumped 30% to 40 492 in October from 31 158 in October 2015. The number of UK tourists increased 14% to 39 696 in October from 34 936 in the same month in 2015. The overall number of foreign tourists visiting SA grew 14% to 850 956 in October from 748 561 in October 2015. The US maintained third place with an 8% growth in tourists to 27 583 with fourth-placed France narrowing the gap with a 22% jump in tourist numbers to 19 009 people. Of the German visitors more than 98% were holiday makers. Four percent of UK visitors were on business trips compared with 3% of US visitors. TMG Digital/BusinessLIVE